name: Hi. I'm Kate.
body:
### Nice to meet you. 

I'm a web developer in Durham, NC.

I'm currently a student at the Ruby on Rails program at [The Iron Yard](https://www.theironyard.com/locations/durham.html), seeking full-time employment as a developer starting in early May, 2016.

In a past life, I was a product and project manager and bring my organizational and planning skills to every problem I approach as a developer. I'm fascinated by the web and all it has to offer, and am excited to help make it a better place.

#### Connect with me
* [GitHub](https://github.com/katestud)
* [LinkedIn](https://www.linkedin.com/in/katestudwell)
* Portfolio
